{"kanda":6,"sarga":61,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"ततोरामोमहातेजाधनुरादायवीर्यवान् ।किरीटिनंमहाकायंकुम्भकर्णंददर्श ह","trans":"On taking up a bow Rama saw Kumbhakarna of extraordinary energy, prodigious, and of large body, adorned with a crown.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"महातेजाः","m":"of extraordinary energy"},{"d":"वीर्यवान्","m":"prodigious"},{"d":"रामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"धनुः","m":"bow"},{"d":"आदाय","m":"taking"},{"d":"किरीटिनम्","m":"adorned with crown"},{"d":"महाकायम्","m":"of large size"},{"d":"कुम्भकर्णम्","m":"Kumbhakarna"},{"d":"ददर्श","m":"saw."}]},{"v":2,"dev":"तंदृष्टवाराक्षसश्रेष्ठंपर्वताकारदर्शनम् ।क्रममाणमिवाकाशंपुरानारायणंप्रभुम्","trans":"That foremost of Rakshasas was like a mountain in appearance, it was like Lord Narayana taking steps to the sky earlier.","words":[{"d":"पर्वताकारदर्शनम्","m":"like a mountain in appearance"},{"d":"पुरा","m":"earlier"},{"d":"आकाशम्","m":"sky"},{"d":"क्रममाणम्","m":"taking steps"},{"d":"प्रभुम्","m":"Lord"},{"d":"नारायणं","m":"Narayana"},{"d":"यथा","m":"so also"},{"d":"तंराक्षसश्रेष्ठम्","m":"that foremost of Rakshasas"},{"d":"दृष्टव","m":"I witnessed."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"सतोयाम्बुदसङ्काशंकाञ्चनाङ्गदभूषणम् ।दृष्टवापुनःप्रदुद्रवावानराणांमहाचमूः","trans":"Seeing the Rakshasa who was like a rainy cloud with water, decked with gold ornaments, the commander in chief of Vanaras ran.","words":[{"d":"सतोयाम्बुदसङ्काशम्","m":"like rainy cloud with water"},{"d":"काञ्चनाङ्गदभूषणम्","m":"decked with gold ornaments"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"वानराणाम्","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"महाचमूः","m":"commander in chief"},{"d":"पुनः","m":"again"},{"d":"प्रदुद्राव","m":"ran."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"विद्रुतांवाहिनींदृष्टवावर्धमानं च राक्षसम् ।सविस्मयमिदंरामोविभीषणमुवाच ह","trans":"Seeing the army scared away and the army of Rakshasas growing in size, Rama was astonished and thus spoke to Vibheeshana.","words":[{"d":"रामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"विद्रुताम्","m":"scared"},{"d":"वाहिनीम्","m":"army"},{"d":"वर्धमानम्","m":"growing big"},{"d":"राक्षसं च","m":"and Rakshasas"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"सविस्मय","m":"astonished"},{"d":"विभीषणम्","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"thus"},{"d":"उवाच ह","m":"spoke."}]},{"v":5,"dev":"कोऽसौपर्वतसङ्काशःकिरीटीहरिलोचनः ।लङ्कायांदृश्यतेवीरःसविद्युदिवतोयदः","trans":"\"Who is that hero resembling a mountain, a crowned one with tawny eyes, looking like a rainy cloud driven by lightning? He is seen in Lanka.\"","words":[{"d":"पर्वतसङ्काशः","m":"resembling mountain"},{"d":"किरीटी","m":"crowned"},{"d":"हरिलोचनः","m":"of tawny eyes"},{"d":"सविद्युत्","m":"by lightning"},{"d":"तोयदःइव","m":"like rainy cloud"},{"d":"वीरः","m":"hero"},{"d":"लङ्कायाम्","m":"at Lanka"},{"d":"दृश्यते","m":"seen"},{"d":"असौ","m":"oh"},{"d":"क","m":"who is he."}]},{"v":6,"dev":"पृथिव्यांकेतुभूतोऽसौमहानेकोऽत्रदृश्यते ।यंदृष्टवावानरास्सर्वेविद्रवन्तिततस्ततः","trans":"\"He is seen here like a lone comet on earth. Seeing him the Vanaras are fleeing hither and thither.\"","words":[{"d":"महान्","m":"remarkable"},{"d":"असौ","m":"he is"},{"d":"एकः","m":"lone"},{"d":"अत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"पृथिव्याम्","m":"earth"},{"d":"केतुभूतः","m":"comet"},{"d":"दृश्यते","m":"appears"},{"d":"यम्","m":"him"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"on seeing"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"वानराः","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"ततस्ततः","m":"hither and thither"},{"d":"विद्रवन्ति","m":"fleeing."}]},{"v":7,"dev":"आचक्षवसुमहान् कोऽसौरक्षोवायदिवाऽसुरः ।न मयैवंविधंभूतंदृष्टपूर्वंकदाचन","trans":"\"Who is he, that gigantic Rakshasa? Is he a demon or perhaps a colossus? No such being was seen by me earlier.\"","words":[{"d":"सुमहान्","m":"gigantic"},{"d":"असौ","m":"he is"},{"d":"क","m":"who"},{"d":"रक्षःवा","m":"that Rakshasa"},{"d":"यदिवा","m":"perhaps"},{"d":"असुरः","m":"demon"},{"d":"आचक्षव","m":"colossus"},{"d":"मया","m":"by me"},{"d":"एवंविधम्","m":"this kind"},{"d":"धूतम्","m":"messenger"},{"d":"कदाचन","m":"not seen"},{"d":"न दृष्टपूर्वम्","m":"not seen earlier."}]},{"v":8,"dev":"संपृष्टोराजपुत्रेणरामेणाक्लिष्टकर्मणा ।विभीषणोम