्तुं न शेकुस्त्रिदशाःकालोऽयमितिमोहिताः","trans":"\"This Kumbhakarna with pike in hand and fierce eyes, is mighty strong. All the Devatas could not kill him, deluded that he is death personified.\"","words":[{"d":"शूलपाणिम्","m":"with pike in hand"},{"d":"विरूपाक्षम्","m":"fierce eyes"},{"d":"महाबलम्","m":"mighty strong"},{"d":"कुम्भकर्णम्","m":"Kumbhakarna"},{"d":"स्त्रिदशाः","m":"all Devatas"},{"d":"अयम्","m":"this"},{"d":"कालःइति","m":"death personified"},{"d":"मोहिताः","m":"deluded"},{"d":"हन्तुम्","m":"to think of killing"},{"d":"न शेकुः","m":"not kill."}]},{"v":12,"dev":"प्रकृत्याह्येषतेजस्वीकुम्भकर्णोमहाबलः ।अन्येषांराक्षसेन्द्राणांवरदानकृतंबलम्","trans":"\"Kumbhakarna is by nature (by birth) energetic and mighty. The strength of other Rakshasas is on account of their boons received by them.\"","words":[{"d":"एषः","m":"in that way"},{"d":"कुम्भकर्णः","m":"Kumbhakarna"},{"d":"प्रकृत्याः","m":"by nature"},{"d":"तेजस्वी","m":"energetic"},{"d":"महाबलः","m":"mighty"},{"d":"अन्येषाम्","m":"of others"},{"d":"राक्षसेन्द्राणाम्","m":"Rakshasa kings"},{"d":"बलम्","m":"strength"},{"d":"वरदानकृतम्","m":"is on account of boons."}]},{"v":13,"dev":"एतेनजातमात्रेणक्षुधार्तेनमहात्मना ।भक्षितानिसहस्राणिसत्त्वानांसुबहून्यपि","trans":"\" As soon as he was born, he was hungry and this great soul being strong consumed thousands of created beings.\"","words":[{"d":"जातमात्रेण","m":"as he was born"},{"d":"क्षुधार्तेन","m":"due to hunger"},{"d":"एतेन","m":"all"},{"d":"महात्मना","m":"great soul"},{"d":"सत्त्वानाम्","m":"created beings"},{"d":"सुबहूनिअपि","m":"being strong"},{"d":"सहस्राणि","m":"thousands"},{"d":"भक्षितानि","m":"were consumed."}]},{"v":14,"dev":"तेषुसंभक्षयमाणेषुप्रजाभयनिपीडिताः ।यान्तिस्मशरणंशक्रंतमप्यर्थंन्यवेदयन्","trans":"\"In that way when Kumbhakarna was devouring, out of fear all people sought the refuge of Indra and represented.\"","words":[{"d":"तेषु","m":"that way"},{"d":"सम्भक्षयमाणेषु","m":"was eating every one"},{"d":"प्रजाः","m":"people"},{"d":"भयनिपीडिताः","m":"out of fear"},{"d":"शक्रम्","m":"Indra"},{"d":"शरणंयान्तिस्म","m":"sought refuge"},{"d":"तम्","m":"they"},{"d":"अर्धम् अपि","m":"all about"},{"d":"न्यवेदयन्","m":"represented."}]},{"v":15,"dev":"सकुन्भकर्णंकुपितोमहेन्द्रोजघानवज्रेणशितेनवज्री ।सशक्रवज्राभिहतोमहात्माचचालकोपाच्चभृशंननाद","trans":"\"Mahendra who was armed with thunderbolt got enraged and hurt Kumbhakarna with thunderbolt. He reeled and roared with the strike.\"","words":[{"d":"वज्री","m":"armed with thunderbolt"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"महेन्द्रः","m":"Mahendra"},{"d":"कुपितः","m":"enraged"},{"d":"कुम्भकर्णम्","m":"Kumbhakarna"},{"d":"वज्रेण","m":"at Indra"},{"d":"जघान","m":"hurt"},{"d":"शक्रवज्राभिहतः","m":"with thunderbolt"},{"d":"महात्मा","m":"great self"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"चचाल","m":"reeled"},{"d":"कोपात्","m":"in anger"},{"d":"भृशम्","m":"intense"},{"d":"ननाद च","m":"roared."}]},{"v":16,"dev":"तस्यनानद्यमानस्यकुम्भकर्णस्यरक्षसः ।श्रुत्वानिनादंवित्रस्ताःभूमिभूयोवितत्रसे","trans":"\"People were already afraid of Kumbhakarna, and after hearing the lion roar of this Rakshasa they were even more scared.\"","words":[{"d":"वित्रस्ताः","m":"alarmed"},{"d":"प्रजाः","m":"people"},{"d":"नानद्यमानस्य","m":"hearing the lion roar"},{"d":"रक्षसः","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"तस्यकुम्भकर्णस्य","m":"that Kumbhakarna's"},{"d":"निनादम्","m":"roar"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"hearing"},{"d":"भूयः","m":"became"},{"d":"वितत्रसे","m":"scared."}]},{"v":17,"dev":"तत्रकोपान्महेन्द्रस्यकुम्भकर्णोमहाबलः ।विकृष्यैरावताद्धन्तंजघानोरसिवासवम्","trans":"\"Then mighty Kumbhakarna, who was enraged, pulled out the tusk of Airavatham and struck at the chest of Indra.\"","words":[{"d":"तत्र","m":"then"},{"d":"महेन्द्रस्य","m":"Mahendra's"},{"d":"कोपात्","m":"anger"},{"d":"महाबलः","m":"mighty"},{"d":"कुम्भकर्णः","m":"Kumbhakarna"},{"d":"ऐरावतात्","m":"Airavatham"},{"d":"दन्तम्","m":"tusk"},{"d":"विकृष्य","m":"tearing"},{"d":"वासवम्","m":"from the mouth"},{"d":"उरसि","m":"chest"},{"d":"जघान","m":"struck."}]},{"v":18,"dev":"कुम्भकर्णप्रहारार्तोविजज्वाल स वासवः ।ततोविषेदुस्सहसादेवाब्रह्मर्षिदानवाः प्रजाभिस्सहशक्रश्चययौस्थानंस्वयम्भुवः ।","trans":"\"Hit by Kumbhakarna Indra felt tormented. The Devatas, Brahmarshis and Danavas became despondent. Accompanied by created beings they complained to Brahma.\"","words":[{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"वासवः","m":"Indra"},{"d":"कुम्भकर्णप्रहारार्तः","m":"for Kumbhakarna's hit"},{"d":"विजज्वाल","m":"tormented"},{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"देवाः","m":"Devatas"},{"d":"ब्रह्मर्षिदानवाः","m":"Brahmarshis, Danavas"},{"d":"सहसा","m":"with force"},{"d":"निषेदुः","m":"despondent"},{"d":"शक्रश्च","m":"Indra's"},{"d":"प्रजाभिःसह","m":"accompanied with created beings"},{"d":"स्वयम्भुवः","m":"to Brahma"},{"d":"स्थानम्","m":"place"},{"d":"ययौ","m":"complained."}]},{"v":19,"dev":"कुम्भकर्णस्यदौरात्म्यंशशंसुस्तेप्रजापतेः प्रजानांभक्षणंचापिधर्षणं च दिवौकसाम् ।आश्रमध्वंसनंचापिपरस्त्रीहरणंभृशम्","trans":"\"They reported to Brahma about Kumbhakarna's ruthless deeds, devouring created beings, insulting, harsh and also destroying the abodes of sages violently and abducting others' wives.\"","words":[{"d":"ते","m":"you"},{"d":"प्रजापतेः","m":"Brahma"},{"d":"कुम्भकर्णस्य","m":"Kumbhakarna's"},{"d":"दौरात्म्यम्","m":"ruthless deeds"},{"d":"प्रजानाम्","m":"created beings"},{"d":"भक्षणंचापि","m":"devouring"},{"d":"दिवौकसाम्","m":"insulting"},{"d":"धर्षणं च","m":"harshness"},{"d":"आश्रमध्वंसनंचापि","m":"also destroying the abodes of sages"},{"d":"भृशम्","m":"violently"},{"d":"परस्त्रीहरणम्","m":"abducted others' wives"},{"d":"शशंसुः","m":"reported."}]},{"v":20,"dev":"कुम्भकर्णस्यदौरात्म्यंशशंसुस्तेप्रजापतेः प्रजानांभक्षणंचापिधर्षणं च दिवौकसाम् ।आश्रमध्वंसनंचापिपरस्त्रीहरणंभृशम्","trans":"\"They reported to Brahma about Kumbhakarna's ruthless deeds, devouring created beings, insulting, harsh and also destroying the abodes of sages violently and abducting others' wives.\"","words":[{"d":"ते","m":"you"},{"d":"प्रजापतेः","m":"Brahma"},{"d":"कुम्भकर्णस्य","m":"Kumbhakarna's"},{"d":"दौरात्म्यम्